{"tid":21441,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖！陽具塞膠樽勃起了 結果拔不出來","createTime":"2016-12-03T23:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T23:28:00.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7a267ad5c6969d12957ffa4c71b1b3898426b33","tid":21441,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:12:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20150630/640_d84140298aec693926bfcb4679b09250.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20150630%2F640_d84140298aec693926bfcb4679b09250.jpg&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6JkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=71b0d963\" target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20150630/640_d84140298aec693926bfcb4679b09250.jpg</a><br />\n英國一名電視醫師傑森(Christian Jessen)近日出示一個病例，表示該名男病患看到「有洞就插」，他把陰莖放進可口可樂的寶特瓶內，隨後達到勃起的效果。但是，生殖器也因此拔不出來，悲劇就這樣發生了。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《都市報》報導，傑森說，男子之後來到他的診所治療，才解除災難。他形容這或許不是最嚴重的案例，但或許是最好笑的。不過，傑森也說，他認為男性生殖器最嚴重的程度應該就是「半折不能直豎」，他說：「你可以試著想像，陰莖折斷後血流滿地，然後看到那腫脹又發紫的『雞雞』。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"6e9de3c5e425515c71584ec6049ab8e73d04588d","tid":21441,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:16:08.000Z","msg":"點先入到個樽?"},{"pid":"e42bfb2d79278145ccca7b71dd8575fdd1c74301","tid":21441,"uid":9964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:24:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20150630/640_d84140298aec693926bfcb4679b09250.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20150630%2F640_d84140298aec693926bfcb4679b09250.jpg&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6JkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=71b0d963\" target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20150630/640_d84140298aec693926bfcb4679b09250.jpg</a><br />\n英國一名電視醫師傑森(Christian Jessen)近日出示一個病例，表示該名男病患看到「有洞就插」，他把陰莖放進可口可樂的寶特瓶內，隨後達到勃起的效果。但是，生殖器也因此拔不出來，悲劇就這樣發生了。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《都市報》報導，傑森說，男子之後來到他的診所治療，才解除災難。他形容這或許不是最嚴重的案例，但或許是最好笑的。不過，傑森也說，他認為男性生殖器最嚴重的程度應該就是「半折不能直豎」，他說：「你可以試著想像，陰莖折斷後血流滿地，然後看到那腫脹又發紫的『雞雞』。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n施旖婕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802b7251f2505593f3201a0e773470b62d9559de","tid":21441,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點先入到個樽?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n牙籤"},{"pid":"3a7ac41362bcf0b676e935e43926e5e06c33ae03","tid":21441,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:28:00.000Z","msg":"41J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}